data.description: One owner 4 bedroom home on cul-de-sac with oversized primary suite complete with a large sitting area and ensuite bathroom featuring separate tub, shower, and double vanities. Separate living room, dining room, eat in kitchen and office on main floor.  Front and rear staircase to 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on 2nd floor. Full unfinished basement stubbed for bathroom provides storage or ready to build out.  New back door installed in October. Community amenities, including swim and tennis.  Convenient to shopping, restaurants, recreation and access to I-85 and Hwy 316.  Come make this your new home!
